OL,3,CLiverpool offer first look at
OL,4,Cpermanent memorial to Diogo Jota
OL,6,FLiverpool FC have released images of a
OL,7,Fnew permanent memorial paying tribute
OL,8,Fto Diogo Jota and his brother Andre
OL,9,FSilva.
OL,11,FThe forward was killed alongside his
OL,12,Fbrother in a car crash in July 2025 as
OL,13,Fhe made his way back to Liverpool for
OL,14,Fpre-season training.
OL,26,@pD@crr
