OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778512268
OL,3,CLiverpool offer first look at
OL,4,Cpermanent memorial to Diogo Jota
OL,6,FThe two Portuguese players will now be
OL,7,Fmemorialised with a permanent
OL,8,Fsculpture outside Anfield titled
OL,9,F"Forever 20", which the club says
OL,10,F"celebrates their lives, their bond,
OL,11,Fand the love and respect felt by
OL,12,Ffamily, teammates and supporters
OL,13,Facross the world."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
