CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778512268
OL,3,CLiverpool offer first look at
OL,4,Cpermanent memorial to Diogo Jota
OL,6,FThe club continued in a statement: "At
OL,7,Fits centre is a flowing heart
OL,8,Fsculpture, in acknowledgement of
OL,9,FDiogo's iconic goal celebration, while
OL,10,Fviewed from different angles it also
OL,11,Freveals the numbers 20 and 30, which
OL,12,Fadorned the back of the brothers'
OL,13,Fplaying shirts.
OL,15,F"It will also feature the lyrics to
OL,16,FJota's famous song so beloved by
OL,17,FLiverpool fans, and one they still
OL,18,Fsing at every game on the 20th minute."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
