OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778512268
OL,3,CLiverpool offer first look at
OL,4,Cpermanent memorial to Diogo Jota
OL,6,FJota died just days after getting
OL,7,Fmarried to his long-term partner Rute
OL,8,FCardoso, and was about to begin pre-
OL,9,Fseason training when he died.
OL,11,FShortly after his death Liverpool fans
OL,12,Fcame to Anfield to pay tribute, with
OL,13,Fhundreds of scarves, flags, and
OL,14,Fflowers left outside the ground.
OL,16,FLiverpool retired Jota's No.20 shirt
OL,17,Fat all levels of the club last season,
OL,18,Fand fans have continued to chant the
OL,19,Fforward's name in the 20th minute of
OL,20,Fevery match.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
