CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778512268
OL,3,CLiverpool offer first look at
OL,4,Cpermanent memorial to Diogo Jota
OL,6,FThere is no date set for the sculpture
OL,7,Fto be properly installed, but the club
OL,8,Fhas confirmed it will be positioned on
OL,9,F97 Avenue close to where tributes were
OL,10,Fpaid shortly after his death.
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
